    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/8c8dabb6cb6385de2d82154efe31da16.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简短故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们以为“灰尘与尘埃的时代”已经结束，但暗影再次苏醒，预言开始发挥作用。月光下诞生的白发少女埃丽娅，是唯一能抗衡堕落之星的人。她在塔顶醒来，举起火焰，踏上抑止席卷世界的恶梦之路。现在，黑暗再次蔓延。<strong>你握着决定命运的刀刃。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新增模式！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验全新加入的Boss挑战模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战强大的Boss，展现你的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/f3c5163349976c6072de31a3f2f86577.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏概览</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Slayer》是一款以精密战斗系统和阴暗剧情为核心的策略动作游戏。仅靠反应速度无法存活——移动方向、位置、攻击角度、格挡时机、闪避、地图结构都需策略性考虑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/e72961f0f5cf8c4d8d3d4a25eb9a603e.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三种游戏模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>动作模式</strong>：可向任意方向攻击，连击爽快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>大师模式</strong>：只能向正面攻击。需要精准站位与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>硬核模式</strong>：生命有限，生命耗尽即灭。极限生存体验模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/1b1d7aacb390ed9687f22f41639d144c.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗与玩法特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 策略型灵魂动作战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 像解谜一样设计的关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 拥有独特机制的Boss战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 短时但高密度的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/b01d28349b26cefd9dbe891a6f9babd4.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>即将推出：亡者模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定于2024年10月更新。这将是一款内容丰富的扩展，拥有新地图、新敌人与Boss、更深层策略与沉重氛围，几乎等同于续作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.poster.avif?t=1762854781\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.webm?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/ca8a3c43be01ff69539d1f246a85c9fe.mp4?t=1762854781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842320/extras/bb5c957b4618ea9b34a150ee578be6a0.avif?t=1762854781\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p>",
